Season: 1937
Competition: Chilean Campeonato de Apertura

Round: First Round
; Magallanes             ; 5-3; Chile Amateur
; Colo Colo                  ; 5-2; Chile B
; Santiago Morning           ; 4-2; Unión Española           
; Audax Italiano                 ; 6-1; Badminton

Round: Semifinals

; Magallanes             ; 5-2; Colo Colo           
; Audax Italiano             ; 1-0; Santiago Morning

Round: Third Place Match
; Colo Colo      ; 4-2; Santiago Morning

Round: Final
; Magallanes             ; 2-0; Audax Italiano

*Magallanes are winners of the Campeonato de Apertura

Competition: Chilean Primera Division
*Campeonato Oficial

*Final Table:
*
* 1.COLO COLO            12  9  3  0  47-20  21    Champions
* 2.Magallanes               12  7  2  3  38-32  16
* 3.Unión Española           12  8  0  4  22-21  16 
* 4.Santiago Morning         12  6  1  5  38-33  13
* 5.Audax Italiano           12  5  2  5  33-34  12
* 6.Badminton                    12  2  2  8  31-49   6
* 7.Santiago Wanderers           12  0  0 12  17-37   0

*NB: six matches were awarded a win (and two points) to a team which had not won it; while this is reflected in the W-D-L records (and point totals), the original results remained valid for the goal records of the teams involved.

*NB: all teams from Santiago de Chile, except Santiago Wanderers (Valparaíso)

